OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FA man has been charged over allegedly
OL,8,Fentering the Carabao Cup final at
OL,9,FWembley without a ticket in the first
OL,10,Fcharge for tailgating at a football
OL,11,Fmatch, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,13,FTailgating, which is when fans get
OL,14,Fthrough stadium turnstiles by walking
OL,15,Fclosely behind ticket holders, became
OL,16,Fa criminal offence ahead of the match,
OL,17,Ffive years after thousands of
OL,18,Fticketless fans stormed the same
OL,19,Fstadium.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
