OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FOffenders across England and Wales who
OL,8,Fare convicted of tailgating face a
OL,9,Ffootball banning order of up to five
OL,10,Fyears as well as a fine of up to
OL,11,F#1,000.
OL,13,FBenjamin Bailey, 27, of Oldham,
OL,14,FManchester, was arrested at Sunday
OL,15,Fafternoon's final between Manchester
OL,16,FCity and Arsenal and charged with
OL,17,Ftailgating hours later at 7.45pm.
OL,19,FHe will appear at Willesden
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court on May 1.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FTwo other men were arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of the same offence at
OL,9,FWembley and remain in police custody.
OL,11,FThere was a 78% reduction in offences
OL,12,Fat this year's final, the Met said.
OL,14,FA total of 20 arrests were made on
OL,15,FSunday compared to 91 arrests at the
OL,16,Fsame fixture last year, the force
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FThe arrests this year included seven
OL,8,Ffor affray, one for assault of an
OL,9,Femergency service worker, and one for
OL,10,Fracially aggravated assault.
OL,12,FA man was also arrested on suspicion
OL,13,Fof tailgating on Sunday at Tottenham
OL,14,FHotspur Stadium as the north London
OL,15,Fteam faced Nottingham Forest, police
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FHe had been bailed pending further
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
