OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FChief Inspector Pete Dearden, from the
OL,8,FMet's public order unit and match
OL,9,Fcommander at Wembley, said: "So much
OL,10,Fstrategic planning goes into these
OL,11,Foperations.
OL,13,F"We expect high standards and every
OL,14,Fofficer delivered that today.
OL,16,F"Huge changes have been implemented
OL,17,Fsince last year, and we will now use
OL,18,Fthe success of the policing operation
OL,19,Ftoday as a blueprint throughout the
OL,20,Fbusy summer at Wembley so fans can
OL,21,Fsafely enjoy upcoming fixtures."
OL,26,@qD@]OUuD@AOUxD@AOU}D@`O]
