FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FThe legislation was introduced
OL,8,Ffollowing serious disorder when
OL,9,FEngland played Italy at the Euro 2020
OL,10,Ffinal.
OL,12,FLives were put at risk when supporters
OL,13,Fbroke into Wembley Stadium, a
OL,14,Fsubsequent review by Baroness Louise
OL,15,FCasey found.
OL,17,FThe new laws follow her findings that
OL,18,Fsanctions on breaking into stadiums
OL,19,Fwere weak and that tailgating should
OL,20,Fbecome a criminal offence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FThere was previously no specific legal
OL,8,Fpenalties for attending a football
OL,9,Fgame without a ticket.
OL,11,FThe Unauthorised Entry to Football
OL,12,FMatches Act also makes it illegal to
OL,13,Fknowingly try to enter a match with
OL,14,Fforged tickets, passes and
OL,15,Faccreditation documents, as well as by
OL,16,Fpretending to be a member of stadium
OL,17,For playing staff.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FIt follows an independent review of
OL,8,Fthe Uefa European Championship final
OL,9,Fheld at Wembley in north London on
OL,10,FJuly 11 2021.
OL,12,FBaroness Casey identified more than 20
OL,13,F"near misses" that could have resulted
OL,14,Fin serious injury or death as a result
OL,15,Fof ticketless individuals trying to
OL,16,Fgain entry, and in some cases
OL,17,Fsucceeding, for the England v Italy
OL,18,Fmatch.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
