OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774368667
OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FAround 100,000 people travelled to
OL,8,FWembley for the final "of which
OL,9,Fapproximately 2,000 gained entry to
OL,10,Fthe stadium without tickets", with 17
OL,11,Fmass breaches of the gates in the 90
OL,12,Fminutes before kick-off until the
OL,13,Fpenalty shootout.
OL,15,FThe new laws also come after problems
OL,16,Fencountered by Liverpool supporters
OL,17,Fduring their Champions League final
OL,18,Fagainst Real Madrid in Paris in 2022.
OL,26,@pD@WOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
