OL,3,CFirst charge for tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match brought by police at
OL,5,CCarabao Cup
OL,7,FIn that instance, authorities were
OL,8,Ffound to be at fault for major
OL,9,Fproblems around the Stade de France
OL,10,Fdespite their attempts to pin the
OL,11,Fblame on Liverpool supporters.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
